126
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:41,240
Everything is fine.

127
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,540
Can I add a dream catching net?

128
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:48,390
When I was a kid, I really wanted this kind of

129
