263
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:19,670
Okay.

264
00:17:21,069 --> 00:17:21,950
Thank you, sir.

265
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:22,869
You're welcome.

266
00:17:22,869 --> 00:17:23,650
